Encrypt_orDecrypt_tools

🔐 Text Encryption or Decryption Tool This is a simple and interactive web-based tool that allows you to encrypt or decrypt text easily. Whether you're learning about cryptography or just want a fun project, this tool provides a clean and functional interface

🚀 Features 💬 Textarea input for any message

🔒 "Encrypt" and "Decrypt" buttons

🌈 Modern and attractive UI with gradient background 📁 Technologies Used HTML

CSS

JavaScript

📦 How to Use Clone the repo or download the code.

Open the html file in any browser.

Type your message.

Click "Encrypt" to convert it into encrypted format.

Click "Decrypt" to revert it back.


